Enum GenericPresets

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<GenericPresets>
      src.enums.GenericPresets
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<GenericPresets>
public enum GenericPresets
extends java.lang.Enum<GenericPresets>

Preset configurations for generic shops. There are up to 20 types of generic shops, each one can have different items available at different prices. This enum will keep track of those preset shop configurations.

Author:
Darren Watts date 1/12/08
